A man has been arrested for allegedly stealing a panties belonging to a pregnant lady. The suspect was nabbed, today, inside the Ibrahim Badamasi Babangida University, Lapai, Niger State and has since been handed over to security operatives. The was subtly beaten and paraded on the streets. Investigations are ongoing to unravel the motive behind the act of theft. In recent times, panties have allegedly being used for money-making rituals. The popular view is that such charm bring good luck to suspected internet fraudsters known as Yahoo Boys. Source